snippet: The National Association of Home Builders/Wells Fargo builder sentiment index, released on Monday, rose this month to 64 points, up from 61 in September.
lead_paragraph: The National Association of Home Builders/Wells Fargo builder sentiment index, released on Monday, rose this month to 64 points, up from 61 in September.

headline.print_headline: U.S. Home Builders Report Highest Confidence In a Decade
